    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Keton Clan, Level 4+</p><p>The light you create shines brighter now holding the ability to blind your foes. You gain the following benefits</p><p>• Increase your Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• Creatures that start their turn or enter a space within multiple sources of bright light you have created must make a Constitution Saving throw against you Ninjutsu DC or gain the Dazzled condition until the beginning of their next turn.</p><p>• While standing in a source of bright light of your own creation, attacks made against you suffer a -1 penalty and you gain a +1 bonus to Dexterity saving throws.</p>",
